<p>SharePoint 2010 is a scalable document repository that blends traditional content management, social computing, and search to deliver an enterprise content management platform. &nbsp;It is quickly becoming the tool of choice for those who want to make information available to <em><strong>authenticated </strong></em>users. &nbsp;Some other capabilities include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Search</li>
<li>Portal</li>
<li>Workflow</li>
<li>Business Intelligence</li>
<li>Enterprise Content Management</li>
<li>Extranet</li>
<li>Intranet
<ul>
<li>The typical intranet is a document repository where users simply uploadand download content. SharePoint offers much more.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Social Networking</li>
<li>...and so on</li>
</ul>
